ndidateKind.appArg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Server</span>.<span class=\"name\">FileWorker</span>.<span class=\"name\">SignatureHelp</span>.<span class=\"name\">CandidateKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">appArg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind\">CandidateKind</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.lean#L61-L65","name":"Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.termArg","line":61,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.termArg","doc":"Cursor is in the position of the trailing whitespace of some term. Medium precedence.\nEnsures that `fun otherFun <cursor>` yields the signature help of `fun`, not `otherFun`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.termArg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Server</span>.<span class=\"name\">FileWorker</span>.<span class=\"name\">SignatureHelp</span>.<span class=\"name\">CandidateKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">termArg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind\">CandidateKind</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.lean#L56-L60","name":"Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.pipeArg","line":56,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.pipeArg","doc":"Cursor is in the position of the argument to a pipe, like `<|` or `$`. Low precedence.\nEnsures that `fun <| otherFun <cursor>` yields the signature help of `otherFun`, not `fun`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind.pipeArg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Server</span>.<span class=\"name\">FileWorker</span>.<span class=\"name\">SignatureHelp</span>.<span class=\"name\">CandidateKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">pipeArg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind\">CandidateKind</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.lean#L55-L70","name":"Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind","line":55,"kind":"inductive","docLink":"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/FileWorker/SignatureHelp.html#Lean.Server.FileWorker.SignatureHelp.CandidateKind\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Server</span>.<span class=\"name\">FileWorker</span>.<span class=\"name\">SignatureHelp</span>.<span class=\"name\">CandidateKind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Server/FileWorker/Signature